data.description: This lovely home has four bedrooms and two full baths. The eat-in kitchen has a large pantry, new granite countertops, new stainless steel appliances, and white cabinets. ALL new flooring- new luxury vinyl plank, with new carpet on the stairs, and fresh paint throughout. Bathrooms have new granite countertops, new toilets, and resurfaced tub/shower combos. The Primary/Master Suite is on the main floor! Three great-sized bedrooms upstairs! Did I mention the NEW ROOF?! Installed last fall. All this on .77 acre IN town! A privacy fence between this home and the one to the right is scheduled for installation. Another great feature for the new owner! Also included is a new storage building in back. Qualifies for FHA, USDA, and VA financing now! Come home to 85 Westview Dr today!
